text.tspan: Time-series data is stored in signal
Data is processed as it is added
The first fftSize points are copied
It is them multiplied by a window function.
The FFT is calculated and the output is stored in ffts
ffts contains arrays with fftSize/2 points.
Arrays contain power from 0 to 0.5/bitrate Hz.
The first step points are deleted from signal, shifting
the next analysis forward. This procedure repeats until
